            <div>
               
	<pb facs="liv_002379_0001" n="0001"/><!-- Change both @facs and @n -->
<lb/><opener><dateline rend="right"><add place="above">28</add> <date when="1865-07-30">30 July 1865</date> <add place="above">72</add>

<!--<lb/><placeName><hi rend="blue" resp="#U2">NEWSTEAD ABBEY,
<lb/>MANSFIELD.
<lb/>NOTTS.</hi></placeName>--> 

<lb/><add place="marginleft">Acc 5973</add></dateline><!-- Change line info as appropriate -->
<lb/>    
<lb/><salute>My Dear D<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Hamilton</salute></opener><!-- Change line info as appropriate -->

<lb/><p>Many thanks
<lb/>for the parcel
<lb/><choice><sic>recieved</sic><corr>received</corr></choice> this 
<lb/>morning - I did
<lb/>not know that 
<lb/>I had left the collars
<lb/>though I thought
<lb/>I had left some
<lb/>for <persName>Agnes</persName> to <gap extent="4" unit="chars" agent="overwriting"/>
<lb/>to the <unclear cert="medium"><term type="occupation">washerwoman</term></unclear>

	<pb facs="liv_002379_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/><persName>Oswell</persName> was upset 
<lb/>about the train
<lb/>and we were just
<lb/>in time. <app><rdg cert="medium"><persName>Woff</persName></rdg><rdg>Webb</rdg></app> is 
<lb/>better - we <app><rdg cert="high">leave</rdg><rdg>have</rdg></app> 
<lb/><persName>Shelley</persName> &amp; <persName>Oswell</persName>
<lb/>&amp; <term type="nationality">African</term> &amp;
<lb/><unclear cert="medium">rocky</unclear> mountains
<lb/>Talk has driven 
<lb/>out the pains &amp;
<lb/>he walks about
<lb/>quite brisk - <persName>M<hi rend="sup">rs</hi>
<lb/><app><rdg cert="medium">Woff</rdg><rdg>Webb</rdg></app></persName> was <app><rdg cert="low">giving</rdg><rdg>grieving</rdg></app>

	<pb facs="liv_002379_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/>me a <unclear cert="low">setting</unclear> this <add place="above">73</add>
<lb/>morning for the
<lb/>going on Tuesday
<lb/>next - she thought
<lb/>I was to be here
<lb/>till startup on 
<lb/>the 11<hi rend="underline">th</hi> I shall
<lb/>go to <placeName><settlement type="town"><unclear cert="low">Sedgwick</unclear></settlement></placeName>
<lb/>Wednesday &amp;
<lb/>pack up on Friday
<lb/>on which might
<lb/>you had better
<lb/>write your friends
<lb/>as must come
<lb/>back - on Saturday

	<pb facs="liv_002379_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/>they are going to
<lb/>keep <persName>Agnes</persName> so 
<lb/>I must come
<lb/>back</p>
<lb/><p>I wonder if 
<lb/><persName>M<hi rend="underline">r</hi> <unclear cert="low">Binney</unclear></persName>
<lb/>would come on
<lb/>that <unclear cert="low">upset</unclear> for it
<lb/>would be impossible
<lb/>for me to go to
<lb/>him for which
<lb/>I am sorry</p>

<lb/><closer><salute>I am &amp;</salute><!-- Change as appropriate -->
<lb/><signed><persName>David Livingstone</persName></signed></closer><!-- Change as appropriate --> 



            </div>
